---
title: Indian Coconut Chicken & Veggie Curry with Basmati Rice
description: Rich, creamy and aromatic – this mild curry has all the elements that make Indian food so appealing. Packed with flavour, it
comes together fast for a mouth-watering meal that the troops will love!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/indian-chicken-kumara-curry-78217327.jpg
